text: The Soccer Ashes is a soccer trophy tournament between Australia and New Zealand. It was first created in 1923 and rediscovered in 2023. It is named after The Ashes test series in cricket between Australia and England. ==List of series== Series Year Host AUS AUS NZL NZL Ref.
